Homemade flour tortillas! Possibly one of the only places in Spanish Harlem that makes their own tortillas. They are known for their quesadillas, but will remain in your memory because of their genuine joy and humble spirit. This place is a foodie gem.  If you find yourself in this part of town, don’t be swayed by the esthetics of other places—go here because the food and the experience is far greater than any other superficial motive.
